 Gabriel and savior flew infront of the cf. They saw magnus being fired upon. 
They took cover behind his armor and watched as his guns started fire. 
Gabriel remembered his special tool against the crazy bot from before. He 
yelled out to all the maximals. "Get behind Magnus and shield your eyes." As 
he said it he pulled a flare bomb from his back and chucked it over the top 
of the truck armor. He watched and pressed the remote denenator as it 
cleared. It should blind all the bots infront of magnus for about 15 seconds.
